Source: picture-rings
Section: web
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Bill MacAllister <bill@ca-zephyr.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 8)
Standards-Version: 3.9.1

Package: picture-rings
Architecture: all
Depends: ${perl:Depends}, libdbi-perl, libdbd-mysql, imagemagick,
 apache2, apache2-mpm-prefork, libapache2-mod-php5, exif,
 libimage-exif-perl, libimage-exiftool-perl
Description: Rings Picture Gallery Web Application
 This web application organizations pictures and displays them via a 
 web server.  The images are loaded into a mysql database in serveral 
 resultions for fast display.  The raw images are stored and not 
 modified.
 .
 The application supports a fine grained access model.  Access control 
 and password information are stored in an LDAP database.
